Package: mmeDetect
Type: Package
Title: Calculate the probability of detection of a mass mortality event
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Justin M. Calabrese and Jesse L. Brunner
Maintainer: Justin M. Calabres <CalabreseJ@si.edu>
Description: Functions for calculating the total probability of detection of
    an MME, given a decay rate and sampling schedule, as well a function for
    calculating the optimal sampling strategy.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
